        <updateDate>2018-09-11T20:46:58Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Comprehensive Screenings for Seniors Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill requires the initial examinations for new enrollees and annual wellness visits under Medicare to include: (1) a screening for potential substance use disorders, and (2) a review of any current opioid prescriptions.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
